OL,6,FHer mother Sharon Rideout said: "She
OL,7,Fcame out of hospital on Saturday and
OL,8,Fhad a terrible night.
OL,10,F"I slept with her and then on the
OL,11,Fmorning of Sunday, I phoned 111 and
OL,12,Fthey eventually came out and said, 'oh
OL,13,Fno, this is normal, she should be
OL,14,Ffine'.
OL,16,F"They left, I said to my mum, I can't
OL,17,Fkeep her here, she needs to go to
OL,18,Fhospital,
