OL,6,F"So she went to hospital in an
OL,7,Fambulance and then by the time they'd
OL,8,Fcome across anything it was all too
OL,9,Flate.
OL,11,F"She ended up in ICU on a Tuesday and
OL,12,Fwe lost her on the Friday. I know she
OL,13,Fhad sepsis before they operated on the
OL,14,FTuesday, she had sepsis, but no one
OL,15,Fever, ever mentioned to us sepsis.
OL,17,F"I just feel if I knew what I know
OL,18,Fnow, it might have been a different
OL,19,Fstory".
