OL,6,F"She actually said to me on the Sunday
OL,7,Fbefore, she said 'I feel like I'm
OL,8,Fgoing to die mum' and I just said,
OL,9,F'Oh, you'll be fine', as you would as
OL,10,Fa mum.
OL,12,F"That is one of the symptoms and so I
OL,13,Fjust think people need to ask the
OL,14,Fquestion always, if you feel unwell,
OL,15,Fyou are the best person to know how
OL,16,Fyou feel and if you don't feel right,
OL,17,Fyou need to go and ask and say, 'do I
OL,18,Fhave sepsis?'"
